# Struktur & Commits

## Astro-Projektstruktur (empfohlen)

```
src/
  components/   → Wiederverwendbare Astro/UI-Komponenten
  layouts/      → Layout-Komponenten (BaseLayout, etc.)
  pages/        → File-based Routing (index.astro, about.astro)
  styles/       → Globale oder geteilte CSS
public/         → Statische Assets (Bilder, Fonts, favicon)
.env.example    → Immer aktuell halten (ohne echte Secrets)
```

## Commit-Messages (Konvention)

```
feat: Add contact form component
fix: Correct meta viewport for mobile
style: Adjust hero spacing
chore: Bump Astro to 6.x
docs: Update README deployment section
```
